summary: This mod replaces the noises that mudcrabs make with the voice of Gil, the ever-so-pinchy crab from the 2006 Honda Element commercial.
descriptionHtml:
This mod replaces the noises that mudcrabs make with the voice of Gil, the ever-so-pinchy crab from the 2006 Honda Element commercial. 

For regular attacks, mudcrabs will say \"I pinch!\" \"I want to pinch!\" and \"Maybe little pinch?\"

When injured, mudcrabs will ask: \"Why no pinch?\"

When killed, mudcrabs will say \"No pinch! No pinch! no... pinch...\"

Hope you guys enjoy.

Special thanks to Tyf-E for giving me the idea with his Posh Mudcrab Voice mod.

Installation:
Drag the \'Data\' folder into your Skyrim root and overwrite. Alternatively you can make things easier by using NMM. Update/Reset Archive Invalidation and you\'re good to go.
author: SneakyD
